Package: SMARTsize
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Sample Size for 2-Stages SMART Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Armando Turchetta <armando.turchetta@mail.mcgill.ca>
Maintainer: Armando Turchetta <armando.turchetta@mail.mcgill.ca>
Description: Provides functions for the Bayesian sample size estimation of a 2-stages SMART study. Please refer to the manuscript following this link for further details: https://arxiv.org/abs/2108.01041.
